<p>
<lb n="1"/>śrī gaṇādhipatayēnamaḥ namastuṁga śirastuṁgiI caṁdracāmara (cā
<lb n="2" break="no"/>mara) cāravē <supplied reason="undefined"><g type="danda">.</g></supplied> traiyilōkya nagarāraṁbha mūlastaṁbhāya śaṁbhavē <supplied reason="undefined"><g type="ddanda">.</g></supplied>
<lb n="3"/>svastiśrī jayābhyudaya kāladalu <hi rend="bold">śakavaruṣa 1<unclear>20</unclear>9 neya vyaya<unclear>saṁva</unclear></hi>
<lb n="4" break="no"/><hi rend="bold">tsarada mārggaśira śuddha 10 vaḍavāradalu</hi> śrī <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> maṁḍaḷēśvara
<lb n="5"/><unclear>Ari</unclear>rāya basavaśaṁkhara śrī <hi rend="bold">vīrapāṁḍya dhanaṁjaya [baṁkidēva Arasa]</hi>
<lb n="6"/><hi rend="bold"> <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> bārakūra rājya</hi>vanāḷuva kāladalu śrī gōpinātha <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> si
<lb n="7"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> paḍuvalu teṁ
<lb n="8" break="no"/>kalu <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> dēvana <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="9"/>raṁ mūḍalu <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> vōṇi<unclear>yiṁ</unclear>
<lb n="10" break="no"/><unclear>daṁ</unclear>tekalu yiṁtīcatusīmeya voḷagāgi nidhinikṣē <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> jala
<lb n="11"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> sahitavāgi sūryyagrahaṇa kāladalu <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="12"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> <note n="362-1">A fragmentary record lying closely and engraved in characters of a slightly later period and therefore probably not connected with the above contains portion of the imprecatory verses which reads:

<l n="27:362:224:1"> <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> </l>

<l n="27:362:224:2"> <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> nyōyaṁ dharmma</l>

<l n="27:362:224:3"> <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> yōbhavaddhi sarvvānētāṁbhā</l>

<l n="27:362:224:4"> <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> yācatē rāmacaṁdraḥ dāna</l>

<l n="27:362:224:5"> <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> pālanaṁ dānāsvarggamavāpnōti</l>

<l n="27:362:224:6"> <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> paradatta vā yō harēti</l></note>
</p>

